{"tid":2507294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西醫工會：領展向屋邨西醫被加租三成 冀集體談判","createTime":"2021-04-28T02:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T02:52:10.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d06ffb59f45fe89404e692d05d1b337043993d39","tid":2507294,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"西醫工會：領展開天殺價提加租三成 冀集體談判<br />\n<br />\n西醫工會領展屋邨診所委員會主席林偉樑表示，領展向屋邨西醫診所提出加租約三成，形容領展「開天殺價」，期望工會能夠與領展就租務問題集體談判。<br />\n<br />\n林偉樑在一個電台節目指，由前年下半年社會運動到去年疫情，西醫診所生意一落千丈。他指，在疫情下市民勤洗手和戴口罩，令傳播機會減少，病人亦擔心診所病人多而會受感染，暫時不到診所看病。他粗略估計，已經有80至100名私家醫生的診所結業。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389194&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0iZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=8d70e8ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389194</a>"},{"pid":"16ab4d7de8fac44cc12ab45a22a13d3cf05f150a","tid":2507294,"uid":356145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:15:54.000Z","msg":"「在疫情下市民勤洗手和戴口罩，令傳播機會減少」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663e359ee6428d3bf8d4a3fbf7b1d1cbb4965da6","tid":2507294,"uid":283970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"正常開響D多廢老既公屋屋邨應該好好生意."},{"pid":"740b95a949a98d59f98a3ff9baa97b66a72f3ac9","tid":2507294,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"663e359ee6428d3bf8d4a3fbf7b1d1cbb4965da6","tid":2507294,"uid":283970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"正常開響D多廢老既公屋屋邨應該好好生意."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:20:17.000Z","msg":"廢老多數長期病睇公立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b528bdd6768f5cd2fa2899aa6e2e8874b8fb35","tid":2507294,"uid":215883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d06ffb59f45fe89404e692d05d1b337043993d39","tid":2507294,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"西醫工會：領展開天殺價提加租三成 冀集體談判<br />\n<br />\n西醫工會領展屋邨診所委員會主席林偉樑表示，領展向屋邨西醫診所提出加租約三成，形容領展「開天殺價」，期望工會能夠與領展就租務問題集體談判。<br />\n<br />\n林偉樑在一個電台節目指，由前年下半年社會運動到去年疫情，西醫診所生意一落千丈。他指，在疫情下市民勤洗手和戴口罩，令傳播機會減少，病人亦擔心診所病人多而會受感染，暫時不到診所看病。他粗略估計，已經有80至100名私家醫生的診所結業。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389194&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0iZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=8d70e8ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389194</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"西醫工會可唔可以成立合作社以集團型式租鋪？"},{"pid":"54b1ecc4c33accdd73b0cedcc1611e7a69b6a473","tid":2507294,"uid":7482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時 唔到三點都唔開鋪啦 <br />\n執左都大把醫院等人用啦"},{"pid":"9faa2d99ec371b4cfc2de3e3fa4f9cafe6aa5d8b","tid":2507294,"uid":112845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}